### **[Documentation](https://www.saqqdy.com/axios-serializer)** **[Change Log](./CHANGELOG.md)** **Read this in other languages: English | [](./README-zh_CN.md)**
## Installing >
comes with the latest version of axios, so you can install it without the

```bash
# use pnpm
$ pnpm install axios-serializer

# use npm
$ npm install axios-serializer --save

# use yarn
$ yarn add axios-serializer
```
, we can use it like this

## Support & Issues

Please open an issue [here](https://github.com/saqqdy/axios-serializer/issues).
